ZH: 我们是乡亲，应该互相帮助。
EN: We are fellow villagers, we should help each other.

ZH: 乡亲们都来参加我妈妈的生日聚会。
EN: All the villagers came to attend my mom's birthday party.

ZH: 乡亲们聚在一起商量如何改善乡村环境。
EN: The villagers gathered together to discuss how to improve the rural environment.

ZH: 我是这个村子的乡亲，你可以告诉我你的问题。
EN: I am a fellow villager in this village, you can tell me your problem.

ZH: 乡亲们筹备了一个文化艺术展览活动。
EN: The villagers organized a cultural art exhibition.

ZH: 乡亲们合作开设了一个小商店，给村民提供生活用品。
EN: The villagers collaborated to open a small store, providing daily necessities for the villagers.

ZH: 我在市区工作，但我仍然常常回乡看望乡亲们。
EN: I work in the city, but I still frequently visit my hometown to see my fellow villagers.

ZH: 乡亲们组织了一次义务植树活动，为村庄增添了绿色。
EN: The villagers organized a voluntary tree-planting activity, adding greenery to the village.

ZH: 乡亲们一起组织了一场农民市集，展示他们的农产品。
EN: The villagers organized a farmers' market together, showcasing their agricultural products.

ZH: 乡亲们齐心协力修复了古老的村庄庙宇。
EN: The villagers worked together to restore the ancient village temple.

ZH: 乡亲们积极参与社区义务工作，共同维护村子的秩序。
EN: The villagers actively participate in community volunteer work, jointly maintaining the order of the village.

ZH: 我们的乡亲和睦相处，形成了一个大家庭。
EN: Our fellow villagers live in harmony, forming a big family.

ZH: 乡亲们举办了一场农民运动会，增强了身体素质。
EN: The villagers held a farmers' sports event, enhancing their physical fitness.

ZH: 夏天，乡亲们会去河边游泳纳凉。
EN: In summer, the villagers will go swimming and enjoy the cool by the river.

ZH: 乡亲们一起草拟了一个发展规划，为村庄未来发展指明方向。
EN: The villagers jointly drafted a development plan, providing a direction for the future development of the village.

ZH: 我们的村子有很多勤劳的乡亲，努力创造美好生活。
EN: Our village has many hardworking fellow villagers who strive to create a better life.

ZH: 乡亲们为迎接节日准备了一场盛大的晚会。
EN: The villagers prepared a grand evening party to celebrate the festival.

ZH: 乡亲们一起举办了一场写生比赛，欣赏大自然的美丽。
EN: The villagers organized a sketching competition together, appreciating the beauty of nature.

ZH: 我是一个移民，但我和这个村子的乡亲们已经建立了深厚的友谊。
EN: I am an immigrant, but I have established a deep friendship with the fellow villagers in this village.
